{"tid":1462053,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]史奈達宣佈掛靴！","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:26:37.000Z","uid":111093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f34773dfe030039b68185af21fa6ab557536c79","tid":1462053,"uid":111093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"Netherlands' Sneijder announces retirement<br />\n<br />\nDutch midfielder Wesley Sneijder has announced his retirement from football after a distinguished career including spells at Ajax, Real Madrid and Galatasaray.<br />\nThe 35-year-old has most recently been in Qatar, playing for Al-Gharafa.<br />\nBut his deal there ended last month, and Sneijder now intends to return to the Netherlands - where he has struck a business deal with Utrecht.<br />\n<br />\nSneijder was part of the dominant Inter team of 2008, which won the Champions League, Serie A and Coppa Italia - and in that year he also picked up a World Cup runners-up medal along with the Silver Ball in South Africa.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eurosport.com/football/football-news-netherlands-wesley-sneijder-announces-retirement_sto7405741/story.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurosport.com%2Ffootball%2Ffootball-news-netherlands-wesley-sneijder-announces-retirement_sto7405741%2Fstory.shtml&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=a2cb8037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eurosport.com/football/football-news-netherlands-wesley-sneijder-announces-retirement_sto7405741/story.shtml</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c0617b7913e88f90e40d1068085a6ba4dd6aba","tid":1462053,"uid":29993,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"未加盟曼聯就掛靴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a032094a559814f75025